<key>G</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Nupi tha cu hlawn nakin a sunglawi deuh, A va cu a si a fahter bal lai
 lo, A nun chung a va ca thatnak lawng a tuah, bochan awk tlak nupi tha a
 si.

[C1]
   A fale nih khan thluachuahnak nu tiah an ti, A va zong nih a
   thang-thatnak lawng a chim &quot;Nupi tha tampi an um si hmanh seh law, Nang
   tluk an um lo ka dawt,&quot; a ti, Iang hi hlen a hmang i dawh hi a ziam kho,
   Bawipa a tihmi nu cu thangthat u, A kut theitlai ruangah khan thangthat
   u, A tuanmi ruangah upat pe u, pe.

[V2]
 Nupi tha hmuh cu a har bel a har ko, Fenh-aih a tah i tirawl a phorh
 hna, Dei hlan in a tho i innchungkhor rian cu, Hlawngtling tein a tuanpi
 tawn hna.

[C2]
   A fale nih khan thluachuahnak nu tiah an ti, A va zong nih a
   thang-thatnak lawng a chim &quot;Nupi tha tampi an um si hmanh seh law, Nang
   tluk an um lo ka dawt,&quot; a ti, Iang hi hlen a hmang i dawh hi a ziam kho,
   Bawipa a tihmi nu cu thangthat u, A kut theitlai ruangah khan thangthat
   u, A tuanmi ruangah upat pe u, pe.

[V3]
 Zaangtlung in rian a tuan i a ngan a dam, Sifak retheimi hna sinah nun
 a siang, Fimnak in a ka a pau i a hmurka ah zaangfah cawnpiaknak kha a um.

[C3]
   A fale nih khan thluachuahnak nu tiah an ti, A va zong nih a
   thang-thatnak lawng a chim &quot;Nupi tha tampi an um si hmanh seh law, Nang
   tluk an um lo ka dawt,&quot; a ti, Iang hi hlen a hmang i dawh hi a ziam kho,
   Bawipa a tihmi nu cu thangthat u, A kut theitlai ruangah khan thangthat
   u, A tuanmi ruangah upat pe u, pe.</lyrics>
<title>NUPI THA CH489</title>
</song>